last_episode_to_air.name: Episode 10: Finals
last_episode_to_air.overview: The Cruiserweight Classic comes to an epic finale! A LIVE two-hour special to determine who is the greatest cruiserweight in the world!

name: WWE Cruiserweight Classic
overview: Many cruiserweight wrestlers from around the world battle in the 32-man tournament.

episodes.name: Episode 1: First Round
episodes.overview: The premiere episode of the Cruiserweight Classic kicks off! Who will prove to be the best in the world?

episodes.name: Episode 2: First Round
episodes.overview: Round 1 of the Cruiserweight Classic rolls on! Who will prove to be the best in the world?

episodes.name: Episode 3: First Round
episodes.overview: Round One of the Cruiserweight Classic continues as THE Brian Kendrick makes his return to WWE, Zack Sabre battles Tyson Dux, and much more!

episodes.name: Episode 4: First Round
episodes.overview: Round 1 of the Cruiserweight Classic comes to a close! Johnny Gargano takes on Tommaso Ciampa, Noam Dar vs. Gurv Sihra and much more!

episodes.name: Episode 5: Second Round
episodes.overview: Round 2 of the Cruiserweight Classic kicks off! Kota Ibushi takes on Cedric Alexander and more! Who will prove to be the best in the world?

episodes.name: Episode 6: Second Round
episodes.overview: Second round action heats up as Akira Tozawa battles Jack Gallagher and Brian Kendrick faces Tony Nese for a spot in the quarterfinals!

episodes.name: Episode 7: Second Round
episodes.overview: Round 2 of the Cruiserweight Classic comes to a close! Rich Swann takes on Lince Dorado and more! Who will move on to the quarter finals?

episodes.name: Episode 8: Quarter Finals
episodes.overview: The greatest in-ring competitors under 205lbs continue their quest to be called the best cruiserweight in the world.

episodes.name: Episode 9: Quarter Finals
episodes.overview: The quarter finals of the Cruiserweight Classic come to a close! Rich Swann takes on TJ Perkins and Zack Sabre Jr. battles Noam Dar!

episodes.name: Episode 10: Finals
episodes.overview: The Cruiserweight Classic comes to an epic finale! A LIVE two-hour special to determine who is the greatest cruiserweight in the world!
